  <div class="tickets-copy page">
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        Tickets include 12 beer tastings, a selection of appetizers at
        Midnight Sun, round-trip transportation and 3.5 hours of stories
        you’ll be sure to recount to your friends back home.
        <br><br>
        Contact us for gift cards, group ticket sales and private event information.
        <br>
        Looking for all the nitty gritty details? <a class="fancybox" rel="group" href="#ticketdetails">Click Here</a>
      </p>
      <div id="ticketdetails">
        <h1>Departure & Arrival</h1>
        We operate 6 days a week, Monday-Saturday.
        <br>
        All tours depart promptly at 2:45 from the pick-up location. We encourage you to arrive 15 minutes early to check in with your Big Swig Hoperator.
        <br>
        The pick-up location is the corner of 4th Ave. and F. St. in downtown Anchorage. If you’re standing by the Visitor Center (the sod-covered log cabin), you’re in the right spot.
        <br>
        After the tour, you will be dropped off at the same corner around 6:30ish. (We say “ish” cause, let’s face it, activities involving beer always run on the “ish clock.”)
        <br><br>
        <h1>What to Bring</h1>
        Please bring your ID with you. You must be 21+ to join the tour. But you knew that already, didn’t you?
        <br>
        Beer and brewery memorabilia will be available for purchase along the way, so bring cash and/or a credit card in case you find a little something that needs to go home with you.
        <br><br>
        <h1>Parking Downtown</h1>
        If you must drive to the pick-up location, note that there are parking garages, paid lots and street parking spots in close proximity.
        <br><br>
        <h1>Swig Responsibly</h1>
        Your safety is everything. If you need transportation after the tour, please talk to your Hoperator. We will be happy to call a cab for you.
        <br><br>
        <h1>Cancellation Policy</h1>
        Hopefully life doesn’t come between you and your brew, but if something pops up and you need to cancel, give us a holler at 907-268-0872 or info@bigswigtours.com.  Cancelations made at least 24 hours before the start of the reserved tour will be eligible for a full refund minus a $6/ticket processing fee. All other cancelations will be charged for the full ticket price.

      </div>
